  <h1>Lasagna</h1>
  <img src="https://www.allrecipes.com/thmb/kxV0VRr4VvRvZnASOqRIE_PkEIg=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/23600-quick-lasagna-DDMFS-4x3-b9924db8f00c4c6d998a73ef9c03df30.jpg" alt="Lasagna" width="400">

  <h2>Description</h2>
  <p>Lasagna is a delicious layered pasta dish with meat, sauce, and cheese baked to perfection. It's a classic comfort food that brings families together around the dinner table.</p>

  <h2>Ingredients</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>12 lasagna noodles</li>
    <li>1 lb ground beef</li>
    <li>2 cups ricotta cheese</li>
    <li>3 cups mozzarella cheese</li>
    <li>2 cups marinara sauce</li>
    <li>1/2 cup Parmesan cheese</li>
    <li>Salt and pepper</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Steps</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).</li>
    <li>Cook noodles and brown the ground beef.</li>
    <li>Layer sauce, noodles, ricotta, beef, and cheese in a baking dish.</li>
    <li>Repeat layers and top with mozzarella and Parmesan.</li>
    <li>Bake for 35–40 minutes. Let rest before serving.</li>
  </ol>

